name: REL(EASE) Katamaran x Iinko
description:
How do you release it? How does it feel like? Is it transcendent? When do you know when it's COMing? 
We all have our own experience of releasing one's feelings.

It's the nature of life. It's the truth. Nobody should be ashamed of it.
Embrace it and enjoy it.
Because we know that when we release it, we feel at EASE.
